{"tid":970230,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"本TG谷有意招收新成員","createTime":"2019-01-05T15:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T08:34:06.000Z","uid":76885,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92ac4e1b13a626b7caaf541e661b2185c42f49ee","tid":970230,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"Hello！我哋嘅TG group誠意招收大家<br />\n本group雖然開谷已久但仍然維持到熱鬧氣氛<br />\n(雖然都有偽毒出曬街變成死寂嘅時候)<br />\n只要你想傾 歡迎隨時插嘴<br />\n唔會局限大家話題亦冇話咩嘢唔講得(十八禁動漫打機話題保證哄動)<br />\n所以非常適合話題多多無所不談嘅你<br />\n而且我哋經常有群聚&amp;小圈子飯聚<br />\n以往舉辦過睇戲團、運動團 、唱K團、飯團、酒團、行山團、文青學術團等等<br />\n大家興趣都非常廣泛 一定搵到你適合你嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\nAdmin會經常處決潛水員<br />\n巴絲比例亦算平均 大約99個巴打之中有1個絲打 <br />\n只希望大家經常上水<br />\n亦冇乜特別規則要大家遵守<br />\n最緊要自重自律<br />\n要搞小圈子 狗衝PM女神<br />\n只要對方唔投訴 admin都唔會干涉<br />\n但公然人身攻擊 性騷擾 引起罵戰就唔好怪admin<br />\n直接踢你都唔需要同你解釋啲乜<br />\n己所不欲 勿施於人<br />\n<br />\n我哋非常期待你嘅加入<br />\n你想講就有人肯聽 你痴線實有人陪你癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nLink：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/BuddyHaHaGroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBuddyHaHaGroup&d=hlyny7b2ObwFXf74lG9jsNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b52c9936\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BuddyHaHaGroup</a>"},{"pid":"fad2c701c57b4add63e810a3386e0714e8ce8cb8","tid":970230,"uid":38503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6d87c7bbd2ca46acb57babe723fc0eb4c62276","tid":970230,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fad2c701c57b4add63e810a3386e0714e8ce8cb8","tid":970230,"uid":38503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}